summary: This is an email chain from September 2021 regarding a travel request for a fact witness to travel to the Southern District of New York (SDNY) for trial preparation in the Maxwell case. The witness was scheduled to meet on August 20, 2021, and planned to travel the day before.

events.title: Witness Trial Prep Meeting
events.description: A fact witness was scheduled to travel to SDNY for trial preparation in the Maxwell case, with a meeting on the morning of this date.

keyFacts: A fact witness was requested to travel to SDNY for trial preparation in the Maxwell case in August/September 2021.
The travel request was made via email on September 8, 2021, referencing a meeting scheduled for August 20, 2021.
The witness planned to fly to New York the day before the meeting and return the same day as the meeting.
The document indicates ongoing trial preparation activities in the Maxwell case as of late 2021.
